      <description>&lt;p&gt;Built as a collaboration of the &lt;a href=&#34;badenlab.org&#34;&gt;Baden lab&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.eye-tuebingen.de/eulerlab/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Euler Lab&lt;/a&gt;, this spatial stimulator is able to use most of the commercially available LEDs, making it quite flexible in terms of wavelength spectra. It can take up to 6 different LEDs and be synchronised with most microscope systems.&lt;/p&gt;
